title: Conan O'Brien headed to Armenia -- for a night
text:
> Entertainment Conan O'Brien headed to Armenia -- for a night FILE - In this Oct. 8, 2015 file photo, Conan O'Brien speaks at the Autism Speaks to LA Celebrity Chef Gala in Santa Monica, Calif. TBS said Monday, Oct. 12, that O'Brien will host his show from Armenia. The episode will air on Nov. 10.
